			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Excuse me.  I think I forgot my jacket."/>
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;What does it look like?
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="It's a simple black jacket."/>
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;Let's see.  Is this yours?
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="No, that's not mine. "/> 
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;I don't see any other jackets.  Wait, is this yours?
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Oh, yes.  It is.  Thanks so much."/>
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;Not at all.]]>
